crud-JAVA
________________________

A simple vanilla CLI JAVA app for incubation interview / certification 

Some concepts worked on this project:

- Interface abstraction
- Classes & Inheritance
- Arrays & OOP  
- Dependency Injection
- Try/catch handling
- Overload

-----------------------

Dependencies: (Linux Environment)

- Make
- OpenJDK 11+

-----------------------

Structure:

.
├── bin (.class Files)
├── Makefile
├── README
├── src
│   ├── cli
│   │   └── CLI.java
│   ├── main.java
│   ├── models
│   │   ├── Person.java
│   │   └── Student.java
│   └── repository
│       ├── FakeRepository.java
│       └── IRepository.java
└── TODO

------------------------

Building:

$ make

-----------------------

Running the Apllication:

$ make run

-----------------------

Display:

Choose one of the following options:            
--------------------------------------
1 - Create person or student                                                                                                                                                                     
2 - Retrieve all persons and students                                                                                                                                                            
3 - Update person/student data                                                                                                                                                                   
4 - Delete person/student                                                                                                                                                                        
5 - Finish operations                                                                                                                                                                            
--------------------------------------          
                                                
